    public static int[] findDiagonalOrder(List<List<Integer>> nums) {
        int rows = nums.size();
        int cols = nums.get(0).size();
        int[][] diagonal = new int[rows + cols - 1][2];
        int index = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < rows; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < cols; j++) {
                diagonal[index][0] = i + j;
                diagonal[index][1] = nums.get(i).get(j);
                index++;
            }
        }
        int[] result = new int[rows * cols];
        for (int i = 0; i < rows + cols - 1; i++) {
            int start = Math.max(0, i - cols + 1);
            int end = Math.min(i, rows - 1);
            while (start <= end) {
                if (diagonal[i][0] - start == i - start) {
                    result[i] = diagonal[i][1];
                    start++;
                } else {
                    result[i] = diagonal[i - 1][1];
                    end--;
                }
            }
        }
        return result;
    }
}
